-- Romanian Utility Calls for Hunedoara Water Network Upgrade Bids
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2013-04-01T13:37:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-01/romanian-utility-calls-for-hunedoara-water-network-upgrade-bids.html
Romanian utility  Apa Prod SA  is
seeking bids for water network upgrades in the western part of
the country under a contract estimated at 57.1 million lei ($16
million).  Bids for the 24-month contract are due May 15, Apa Prod
said in a March 30  procurement notice  on the European Unionâ€™s
tender website. The contract includes water and sewage
infrastructure upgrade works in the towns of Brad, Criscior and
Bucuresci in the western Hunedoara County, according to the
utility.  To contact the reporter on this story:
